commit.message: Use a sparser matrix

Some minor modifications to .travis.yml (#835)

* rename trunk to master

* remove libgdal-dev

* gdal version check to allow beta and rc versions

* add pip freeze after fiona installation

* add --with-webp=no to gdal install

New build matrices and configs (#833)

* New build matrix

Python 2.7 and GDAL 1.11 are removed.

Pythons 3.7 and 3.8 and GDAL nightly are added.

* Rename nightly to 3.1.0

* Resolve leftover conflict in proj install script

* Drop GDAL versions before 2.3, add pythons 3.6 and 3.8

* Update dev requirements

* Allow 3.1.0 (GDAL master) to fail

* Don't update dependencies beyond requirements-dev

* Restore comment

* No need to ignore python 2.7 warnings anymore

* Streamline Travis build

* Remove GDAL 3.0 from allowed failures
